result.formatted_address: B/F & G/F (portion) 16 Elgin Street Central, Hong Kong, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Mo Bros Bar

reviews.text: Good Italian food just off the street, might be hard to see. Friendly staff, indoor and outdoor seating. Reasonable prices and good food + wine.

I visit this place quite often and i always enjoy the veal parmesan. I haven't had a bad experience yet. 

The outside seating is great in the warmer weather and the staff are always helpful.
Quite decent Italian food at a reasonable price.
Is it Forlini’s? No. But it hit my penne arrabiata craving well enough. And for Hong Kong that’s not nothing.
Nice staff. Good food. Have outdoor seating welcome dogs
